title: Misfortunate Reincarnation ~ Otherworldly Orphan Will Rise in the World ~ - Novel Updates

description:
I, an elite researcher in modern Japan, has somehow reincarnated into another world! And the standard of living in this new world is too low!

This story is about a protagonist who lived a golden life, but reincarnated into a poor life in another world, she aims to rise to the top (or at least to the middle-class)>
